Class OracleEdgeBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.common.OracleElementBase
      • oracle.pg.common.OracleEdgeBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OracleElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OracleEdge, OracleEdge

    public abstract class OracleEdgeBase
extends OracleElementBase
    This class implements the Blueprints Edge and Edge interface by using one of the supported backend database.
